<section id="services-hero-532"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-29-13dd8fc0.jpeg" height="775" width="1920" fetchpriority="high"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-card"><div class="cs-heading-group"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Serving Anthony, NM Since 2005</span><h1 class="cs-title">Landscaping Services in <span class="cs-color">Anthony, NM</span></h1></div><p class="cs-text">Drought-tolerant landscape design, hardscaping, irrigation, and xeriscaping for Anthony and the lower Mesilla Valley. Built for river valley soils, salt buildup, and the desert heat of Doña Ana County.</p><div class="cs-button-group"><a class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button" href="/contact/">Schedule an Estimate</a> <a class="cs-phone-button" href="tel:575-635-8883"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/phone.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> (575) 635-8883</a></div></div></div></section><section id="services-intro-109"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern cs-fern-right"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern cs-fern-left"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-row"><img alt="Fresh sod lawn install in Anthony, NM near the lower Mesilla Valley" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-sod-1-1312ad4d.jpeg" height="456" width="480" loading="lazy"><div class="cs-content"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Why Anthony</span><h2 class="cs-title">Rooted in the Lower Valley</h2><p class="cs-text">Anthony sits about 25 minutes south of Las Cruces, right along the New Mexico-Texas state line. It’s a small border community in Doña Ana County with a mix of newer housing developments and older agricultural properties. Many lots here were once farmland, and some still have irrigation ditches running through them. That history shapes the soil, the drainage, and the way we design landscapes here.</p><p class="cs-text">Our crew drives down from Las Cruces regularly to serve Anthony, La Union, Berino, and Chamberino. We know the heavy clay soils near the Rio Grande. We understand the salt buildup from decades of flood irrigation. And we build landscapes that work with these conditions, not against them. No guesswork, no generic plans.</p><div class="cs-button-group"><a class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button" href="/contact/">Schedule an Estimate</a> <a class="cs-phone-button" href="tel:575-635-8883"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/phone.svg" height="13" width="13" aria-hidden="true"> (575) 635-8883</a></div></div></div></div></section><section id="areas-services-610"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> What We Do Here</span><h2 class="cs-title">Services Available in Anthony</h2></div><div class="cs-grid"><ul class="cs-card-group"><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-landscape-design.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Landscape Design</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Custom plans designed for Anthony’s river valley soils, former agricultural lots, and desert sun exposure.</p><a class="cs-item-link" href="/services/landscape-design/">Learn More <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" height="14" width="14" aria-hidden="true"></a></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-landscaping.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Landscaping &amp; Install</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Full-property planting, grading, and installation built to handle heavy clay and salt-affected lower valley soil.</p><a class="cs-item-link" href="/services/landscaping/">Learn More <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" height="14" width="14" aria-hidden="true"></a></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-hardscaping.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Hardscaping &amp; Patios</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Patios, retaining walls, and flagstone work engineered for clay soils and monsoon season drainage.</p><a class="cs-item-link" href="/services/hardscaping/">Learn More <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" height="14" width="14" aria-hidden="true"></a></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-xeriscaping.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Xeriscaping</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Water-wise design with Desert Willow, Red Yucca, and salt-tolerant natives suited to the lower valley.</p><a class="cs-item-link" href="/services/landscaping/xeriscaping/">Learn More <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" height="14" width="14" aria-hidden="true"></a></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-irrigation.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Irrigation &amp; Sprinkler</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Drip systems and smart controllers that account for Anthony’s higher water table and old acequia lines.</p><a class="cs-item-link" href="/services/irrigation/">Learn More <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" height="14" width="14" aria-hidden="true"></a></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-maintenance.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Landscape Maintenance</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Seasonal cleanup, pruning, and drainage checks for residential and commercial properties in Anthony.</p><a class="cs-item-link" href="/services/landscape-maintenance/">Learn More <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" height="14" width="14" aria-hidden="true"></a></li></ul><aside class="cs-area-info"><h3 class="cs-area-title">One Call, One Crew, All Six Services</h3><p class="cs-area-text">Many Anthony properties need more than one specialty. A xeriscape needs irrigation. A patio needs proper drainage. A design needs install. Bundling everything under one team keeps your timeline, budget, and guarantee in a single place.</p><ul class="cs-area-bullets"><li><span class="cs-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" width="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 7.5 L5.5 11 L12 3.5"></path></svg> </span>Design-build under one roof</li><li><span class="cs-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" width="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 7.5 L5.5 11 L12 3.5"></path></svg> </span>Workmanship guarantee</li><li><span class="cs-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" width="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 7.5 L5.5 11 L12 3.5"></path></svg> </span>Las Cruces crew, short drive to Anthony</li></ul></aside></div></div></section><section id="areas-landmarks-620"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-row"><div class="cs-content"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Where We Work</span><h2 class="cs-title">Neighborhoods &amp; Communities We Serve</h2><p class="cs-text">We cover Anthony and the surrounding lower valley communities. From new subdivisions along NM-478 to older homesteads near Berino, we handle every property type in this part of Doña Ana County.</p><div class="cs-button-group"><a class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button" href="/contact/">Schedule an Estimate</a> <a class="cs-phone-button" href="tel:575-635-8883"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/phone.svg" height="13" width="13" aria-hidden="true"> (575) 635-8883</a></div></div><img alt="Newly laid sod backyard lawn in the Anthony, NM area" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-sod-2-4e0a9ee7.jpeg" height="480" width="580" loading="lazy"></div><ul class="cs-neighborhoods"><li class="cs-neighborhood"><h3 class="cs-neighborhood-title">Anthony Proper <span class="cs-neighborhood-zip">88021</span></h3><p class="cs-neighborhood-text">The town center with a mix of established homes and newer developments. River valley clay soil and old irrigation lines are common here.</p></li><li class="cs-neighborhood"><h3 class="cs-neighborhood-title">La Union <span class="cs-neighborhood-zip">88021</span></h3><p class="cs-neighborhood-text">A small agricultural community just north of Anthony. Large lots, pecan orchards, and properties with acequia access that need thoughtful grading.</p></li><li class="cs-neighborhood"><h3 class="cs-neighborhood-title">Berino Area <span class="cs-neighborhood-zip">88024</span></h3><p class="cs-neighborhood-text">Rural properties between Anthony and Las Cruces. Former farmland with fertile but salty soil that benefits from xeriscaping and drip irrigation.</p></li><li class="cs-neighborhood"><h3 class="cs-neighborhood-title">Chamberino <span class="cs-neighborhood-zip">88027</span></h3><p class="cs-neighborhood-text">A quiet farming community along the Rio Grande. Properties here often have high water tables and need drainage planning before any landscape work.</p></li><li class="cs-neighborhood"><h3 class="cs-neighborhood-title">NM-478 Corridor <span class="cs-neighborhood-zip">88021</span></h3><p class="cs-neighborhood-text">The main road through the lower valley with newer residential subdivisions and small commercial properties. Clean-slate lots ready for full landscape installs.</p></li></ul></div></section><section id="services-why-353" class="cs-why-light"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper">Local Know-How</span><h2 class="cs-title">What Makes Anthony Landscapes Different</h2><p class="cs-intro">Anthony sits at a lower elevation than Las Cruces, close to the Rio Grande. That means slightly warmer temperatures, heavier clay soil from river deposits, and salt buildup from decades of agricultural irrigation. Every design choice we make here accounts for those conditions.</p></div><div class="cs-gallery" aria-hidden="true"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-22-f01c10a6.jpeg" height="594" width="460" loading="lazy"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-xeriscaping-19-08d1a3c1.jpeg" height="439" width="330" loading="lazy"></div><ul class="cs-feature-list"><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Heavy Clay &amp; River Soil</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">The lower valley has fertile, river-deposited soil. But it’s dense clay that drains slowly. We amend beds and build raised planters when needed so roots don’t sit in standing water.</p></li><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Salt Buildup in Soil</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">Decades of flood irrigation left salt deposits in many Anthony properties. We test soil before planting and choose salt-tolerant species like Fourwing Saltbush and Desert Willow that handle these conditions.</p></li><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Old Irrigation Ditches &amp; Acequias</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">Many properties still have acequia lines or old irrigation ditches crossing the yard. We work around active easements and can remove or reroute unused ditches as part of your landscape plan.</p></li><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Higher Water Table</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">Near the Rio Grande, the water table can be surprisingly close to the surface. We check depth before setting fence posts, building retaining walls, or planting deep-rooted trees to avoid problems later.</p></li></ul><a class="cs-quote-button" href="/contact/">Schedule an Estimate</a></div></section><section id="testimonials-515" class="cs-reviews-carousel"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/leaves-pattern-8329654d.jpeg" height="1072" width="1920" loading="lazy"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><div class="cs-content"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Testimonials</span><h2 class="cs-title">Let’s Talk About Your Outdoor Vision</h2></div><div class="cs-controls"><button class="cs-arrow cs-arrow-prev" aria-label="Previous reviews" type="button" data-reviews-prev=""><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></button> <button class="cs-arrow cs-arrow-next" aria-label="Next reviews" type="button" data-reviews-next=""><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></button></div></div><ul class="cs-card-group" data-reviews-track=""><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" role="img"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"></div><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/quote-green.svg" height="51" width="51" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-quote-icon"><blockquote class="cs-item-text">David was incredibly knowledgeable and helpful. He patiently answered all of my questions about the plants and trees around my home and provided valuable insights into the issues I was facing. His friendly demeanor and expertise made the experience enjoyable and informative. I highly recommend him</blockquote><div class="cs-item-footer"><div class="cs-author"><span class="cs-name">Alexis Silva</span> <span class="cs-role">a year ago</span></div><a class="cs-google-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103948667181155023139/reviews" aria-label="View review on Google" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/google-g.svg" height="30" width="30"></a></div></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" role="img"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"></div><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/quote-green.svg" height="51" width="51" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-quote-icon"><blockquote class="cs-item-text">We had a great experience with David. We used him for one of our rental properties in Las Cruces and will definitely be using him again for the next one. Everything from start to finish was professional and timely. Highly recommend.</blockquote><div class="cs-item-footer"><div class="cs-author"><span class="cs-name">Travis Boyle</span> <span class="cs-role">a year ago</span></div><a class="cs-google-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108997149124684397289/reviews" aria-label="View review on Google" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/google-g.svg" height="30" width="30"></a></div></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" role="img"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"></div><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/quote-green.svg" height="51" width="51" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-quote-icon"><blockquote class="cs-item-text">Brainard's Greenscapes recently revamped my backyard with rock landscaping. I couldn't be happier with how the project turned out. From start to finish David's team was professional, punctual, and courteous. They helped me select the the right materials and offered additional design ideas. The quality of work was EXCELLENT. I highly recommend David's team to all homeowners in Las Cruces looking for reliable landscaping company. The picture below is of my backyard 1 year later and there is still no weeds! I can't think Braindard's Greenscapes enough.</blockquote><div class="cs-item-footer"><div class="cs-author"><span class="cs-name">Matthew Lee</span> <span class="cs-role">a year ago</span></div><a class="cs-google-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112275232644298872770/reviews" aria-label="View review on Google" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/google-g.svg" height="30" width="30"></a></div></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" role="img"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"></div><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/quote-green.svg" height="51" width="51" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-quote-icon"><blockquote class="cs-item-text">I had a sprinkler emergency and David came out immediately; found an effective solution to get me through until the major repairs could be made; and took care to make sure my house wasn't without water in the meantime. I am so grateful for his kindness and professionalism. He demonstrated considerable expertise and decisive decision making that got me through this emergencies with minimal stress. He is trustworthy and will be the first one I'll call on any future sprinkler needs.</blockquote><div class="cs-item-footer"><div class="cs-author"><span class="cs-name">Jennifer Wees-Schkade</span> <span class="cs-role">2 years ago</span></div><a class="cs-google-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113879630740524577871/reviews" aria-label="View review on Google" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/google-g.svg" height="30" width="30"></a></div></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" role="img"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/star-green.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"></div><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/quote-green.svg" height="51" width="51" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-quote-icon"><blockquote class="cs-item-text">Brainard’s Greenscapes is a top notch business. I have called on them on several occasions to fix issues with my irrigation system and for new projects. David, the owner, is a sincere, honest individual, who cares about his business and his customers. His employees are also kind and always professional. They are punctual and complete the job as promised and clean up after they are done. I am very pleased with David and his company and have recommended him to my neighbor, who is also a widow because I know he is honest and will not take advantage of her. David is a good guy and I recommend that you give him a call and see for yourself.</blockquote><div class="cs-item-footer"><div class="cs-author"><span class="cs-name">George Rodriguez</span> <span class="cs-role">6 years ago</span></div><a class="cs-google-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113926776793747685994/reviews" aria-label="View review on Google" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/google-g.svg" height="30" width="30"></a></div></li></ul></div></section><section id="areas-projects-630"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Case Studies</span><h2 class="cs-title">Anthony Project Showcase</h2></div><ul class="cs-project-group"><li class="cs-project"><img alt="Farmland-to-landscape conversion in progress in Anthony, NM" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-misc-3-705b5b32.jpeg" height="411" width="616" loading="lazy"><h3 class="cs-project-title">Farmland-to-Yard Conversion</h3><p class="cs-project-text">Turned a former irrigated lot into a low-water xeriscape with gravel paths, native plantings, and a drip system.</p></li><li class="cs-project"><img alt="Flagstone patio install in the lower Mesilla Valley" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-patios-7-0cf9763c.jpeg" height="411" width="616" loading="lazy"><h3 class="cs-project-title">Lower Valley Patio &amp; Drainage Fix</h3><p class="cs-project-text">Installed a flagstone patio with French drains to manage clay soil pooling on a property near the Rio Grande.</p></li></ul></div></section><section id="faq-506"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-content"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> FAQ</span><h2 class="cs-title">Anthony Landscaping FAQ</h2></div><ul class="cs-faq-list"><li class="cs-faq-item"><details class="cs-faq"><summary class="cs-faq-summary"><span class="cs-faq-question">Do you travel to Anthony from Las Cruces?</span> <span class="cs-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></span></summary><div class="cs-faq-body"><p>Yes. Anthony is about 25 minutes south of our Las Cruces base. We send a full crew with all equipment, so the drive does not add cost to your project. We work in Anthony, La Union, Berino, and Chamberino on a regular basis.</p></div></details></li><li class="cs-faq-item"><details class="cs-faq"><summary class="cs-faq-summary"><span class="cs-faq-question">Can you remove old irrigation ditches from my property?</span> <span class="cs-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></span></summary><div class="cs-faq-body"><p>If the ditch is no longer active and there is no acequia easement, we can fill, grade, and landscape over it. For active acequia lines, we design around them and keep required setbacks. We check with the local acequia commission before starting any work near a ditch.</p></div></details></li><li class="cs-faq-item"><details class="cs-faq"><summary class="cs-faq-summary"><span class="cs-faq-question">How do I deal with salty soil in the lower valley?</span> <span class="cs-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></span></summary><div class="cs-faq-body"><p>We start with a soil test to measure salt levels. From there, we choose salt-tolerant plants like Fourwing Saltbush, Desert Willow, and Bermuda grass. In planting beds, we amend the soil with gypsum and organic matter to improve drainage and flush salts below the root zone.</p></div></details></li><li class="cs-faq-item"><details class="cs-faq"><summary class="cs-faq-summary"><span class="cs-faq-question">What are the best trees for the Anthony area?</span> <span class="cs-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></span></summary><div class="cs-faq-body"><p>Desert Willow and Chitalpa do well in Anthony’s heat and tolerate salty clay soil. For shade, we recommend Chilean Mesquite or Afghan Pine. Pecan trees also grow naturally in the lower valley if you have enough space and water for them.</p></div></details></li><li class="cs-faq-item"><details class="cs-faq"><summary class="cs-faq-summary"><span class="cs-faq-question">Do you do commercial landscaping for businesses in Anthony?</span> <span class="cs-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></span></summary><div class="cs-faq-body"><p>Yes. We handle commercial landscape installs and maintenance for businesses along the NM-478 corridor and throughout the Anthony area. This includes parking lot islands, entrance plantings, irrigation systems, and ongoing maintenance plans.</p></div></details></li></ul></div></section><section id="areas-stats-640"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><div class="cs-heading-col"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Our Coverage Area</span><h2 class="cs-title">Where We Work in Anthony</h2></div><div class="cs-copy-col"><p class="cs-text">On the map below: our Anthony service area, covering the town center, La Union, Berino, Chamberino, and the NM-478 corridor through the lower Mesilla Valley.</p><a class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button" href="/contact/">Schedule an Estimate</a></div></div><div class="cs-map" aria-label="Map of Anthony, NM service area"><iframe allowfullscreen="" height="430" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade" src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Anthony+NM&amp;z=13&amp;output=embed" title="Map of Anthony, NM service area" width="1280"></iframe></div><ul class="cs-stats"><li class="cs-stat"><span class="cs-stat-number">500+</span> <span class="cs-stat-label">Valley Projects</span></li><li class="cs-stat"><span class="cs-stat-number">19+</span> <span class="cs-stat-label">Years in the Valley</span></li><li class="cs-stat"><span class="cs-stat-number">5/5</span> <span class="cs-stat-label">Average Rating</span></li><li class="cs-stat"><span class="cs-stat-number">100%</span> <span class="cs-stat-label">Quality Guarantee</span></li></ul></div></section><section id="areas-neighbors-660"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Nearby</span><h2 class="cs-title">Neighboring Areas We Serve</h2><p class="cs-text">We also handle landscape projects in nearby Mesilla Valley communities just minutes away.</p></div><ul class="cs-neighbors"><li class="cs-neighbor"><a class="cs-neighbor-link" href="/service-areas/las-cruces-nm/"><span class="cs-neighbor-name">Landscaping in Las Cruces, NM</span><span class="cs-neighbor-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></li><li class="cs-neighbor"><a class="cs-neighbor-link" href="/service-areas/sunland-park-nm/"><span class="cs-neighbor-name">Landscaping in Sunland Park, NM</span><span class="cs-neighbor-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></li><li class="cs-neighbor"><a class="cs-neighbor-link" href="/service-areas/mesilla-park-nm/"><span class="cs-neighbor-name">Landscaping in Mesilla Park, NM</span><span class="cs-neighbor-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></li><li class="cs-neighbor"><a class="cs-neighbor-link" href="/service-areas/mesilla-nm/"><span class="cs-neighbor-name">Landscaping in Mesilla, NM</span><span class="cs-neighbor-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></li></ul></div></section><section id="lets-talk-318"><img alt="" d